{"parentUuid":"fdbe944b-27dd-4c6a-b447-ab0a9c3e5fb4","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"eb95499f-46b9-4d8b-9c64-c413a430d7e6","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"好的\" (OK). They want me to change the default image viewer from the buggy \"Photos\" app to something more stable. Let me set the default PNG opener to \"Windows Photo Viewer\" (which is more stable than the modern \"Photos\" app) or \"Paint\".\n\nActually, let me use \"Windows Photo Viewer\" since it's the classic, stable image viewer. But on Windows 10, it might be hidden. Let me check if it's available, or use \"Paint\" as a fallback.\n\nActually, setting file associations via registry/command line is a bit involved. The simplest approach is to:\n1. Set PNG files to open with Windows Photo Viewer (if available) or Paint\n2. Or use the `ftype` and `assoc` commands\n\nLet me check what's available and set it up.\n\nWindows Photo Viewer is usually available at:\n- `C:\\Program Files\\Windows Photo Viewer\\PhotoViewer.dll`\n- It's launched via `rundll32.exe \"%ProgramFiles%\\Windows Photo Viewer\\PhotoViewer.dll\", ImageView_Fullscreen <file>`\n\nActually, the simplest thing to do is set the association via a registry command. Let me use `ftype` to set the PNG file association to open with Windows Photo Viewer.\n\nBut actually, a simpler approach: let me just set the user's default program for .png files to Windows Photo Viewer or Paint. Let me check if Windows Photo Viewer is enabled on this system first.\n\nActually, the most practical approach for the user is to just set the default app for .png files. Let me use the `Set-UserFTA` or direct registry approach.\n\nHmm, this is getting complex. Let me just suggest the simplest path forward:\n1. Tell the user to right-click → Open with → Choose another app → Windows Photo Viewer → Always\n\nOr I can try to set it programmatically. Let me check if Windows Photo Viewer is available.","signature":"eb95499f-46b9-4d8b-9c64-c413a430d7e6"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":194,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":103936,"output_tokens":1083,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"83a422d5-55b1-45c8-9e78-882a9ca7b3d6","timestamp":"2026-05-18T03:54:08.960Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\ClaudeWorkspace","sessionId":"94a964f0-4e4c-4411-a9de-f74c691550d6","version":"2.1.143","gitBranch":"main"}
