{"parentUuid":"453bbd88-18ae-492c-b2c7-e75a6886c043","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"e007a5c1-8a22-47eb-89cd-30cc41bca671","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到关键线索了。诊断结果：\n\n**\"此电脑\"里挂了一个百度网盘的扩展** (`{679F137C}`)，它把自己注册在了\"此电脑\"的命名空间里。百度网盘的壳扩展（shell extension）经常出这种问题——连不上服务器或者认证过期时，Explorer 枚举到它就卡死。绿条永远走不完、白图标、点击就冻住，都是它的典型症状。\n\n另外你的桌面文件夹搬家可能触发了整个命名空间的重建，百度网盘扩展在这个过程中挂掉了。\n\n**修复方案**：把这个百度网盘扩展从\"此电脑\"里临时移除（不卸载百度网盘本身，只是不让它出现在此电脑页面里）。如果此电脑恢复正常，就确认是它的问题。\n\n要不要试？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1291,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":132608,"output_tokens":890,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"df91657f-e306-47eb-90af-b989a6693e76","timestamp":"2026-05-18T04:32:57.112Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"D:\\ClaudeWorkspace","sessionId":"94a964f0-4e4c-4411-a9de-f74c691550d6","version":"2.1.143","gitBranch":"main","slug":"c-d-d-structured-thimble"}
